      <title>保罗·辛格 (Paul Singer) 力推华尔街自己的“让美国再次伟大”品牌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-25/paul-singer-s-push-for-wall-street-s-own-brand-of-maga-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[对冲基金亿万富翁保罗·辛格 (Paul Singer) 带领一群商界大鳄在过去十年中向曼哈顿政策研究所 (Manhattan Institute for Policy Research) 投入了近 2 亿美元，该研究所是纽约的一家智库，已成为美国右翼思想的集结地。西蒙妮·福克斯曼 (Simone Foxman) 在彭博电视台报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-25/paul-singer-s-push-for-wall-street-s-own-brand-of-maga-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 14:27:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃及计划进口 12 亿美元能源以结束停电</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/egypt-plans-1-2-billion-of-energy-imports-to-end-power-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃及已拨款 11.8 亿美元用于额外能源进口，以期在 7 月底之前消除计划中的停电现象，并解决因气温飙升而给数百万人带来痛苦的问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/egypt-plans-1-2-billion-of-energy-imports-to-end-power-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 14:21:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
